          },
          "reviewBody": "SPANDAN , as it named , Event was Vibrating and pulsating.\nIt was mesmerized performance.\nWay it was scripted , directed and performed was so good and professional.\nMy son in grade 7 Halley. It was hard to believe that Performers are student of middle wing I.e 6/7/8 th class.\nOrganising with so many  events ,era of music  with so many students,  Hats off to teachers, mentors ,organisers and whole team.\nI congratulate MRIS Charmwood team  for successful annual day. Thank you so much .\n\nKanchan Kalra",
          "publisher": {
